      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute gem! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such good care of this beauty, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014not a scratch or a worry in sight! It drives like an absolute dream and I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very happy. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been totally babied and is ready for the road, this is the one! Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
