    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in mechanical harmony, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six with its high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing and individual throttle bodies operating at precise factory tolerances. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring surgical torque distribution. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid with preemptive subframe reinforcement and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation. Every bushing, seal, and dampening component remains in peak operational condition, offering a high-revving, naturally aspirated experience that pulls flawlessly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Truly a collector-grade specimen for the driving purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
