      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint glow. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of creases or wear, while the dashboard and trim retain their factory-fresh luster. Mechanically, this car is flawless, having been maintained exclusively by certified specialists with a comprehensive folder of service records included. It has been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather. From the crisp, immediate response of the engine to the immaculate undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot.",
